# 6. Security Solutions {#_computer_systems_security_planning_for_success.xhtml__security_solutions}
To help combat security breaches, many different vendors offer security solutions. These may be hardware or software

designed to help mitigate a security threat. Security solutions may be created in-house, created custom by a third

